fields.name: Casual Horde Guild
fields.description: We are a casual Horde guild. We play for fun, do some normal raids and mythic+ dungeons. No pressure, just good times. Everyone is welcome!

fields.name: Fellowship of Stormwind
fields.description: We are a social guild. We chat, quest, level, and sometimes raid. Perfect for players who want friends and no stress.

fields.name: Dragons of Azeroth
fields.description: We raid twice a week and do Mythic+ keys daily. We also like fun runs and old raid farming. Good for players who want both progress and chill.

fields.name: Moonlight Clan
fields.description: We are a small friendly guild. We like questing, dungeons, and chatting. We don't rush, just enjoy the game together.

fields.name: Key Runners
fields.description: We are all about Mythic+ keys. We push high keys daily and help each other gear up. If you love dungeons more than raids, this is your home.

fields.name: Knights of Elwynn
fields.description: We are a roleplay guild. We create stories, events, and adventures together in the Alliance lands. Perfect for players who love RP and immersion.
